      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Steve Blincoe</b>\n</p><p><b>Steve Blincoe</b>,<br />\nan American accountant, chess and computer chess aficionado, and one of the Worlds leading collectors of <a href=\"/Dedicated_Chess_Computers\" title=\"Dedicated Chess Computers\">dedicated chess computers</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> as well as programs and accessories <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>. He served multiple times as moderator in <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Blincoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=365247\">Dedicated-Stand Alone- Chess Computers wanted</a> by steven blincoe, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 15, 2004</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://hiarcs.net/forums/viewtopic.php?t=457&amp;sid=08b4092216f74f35a5be63cc34c05f4f\">Collector's Corner..I Dont Think So..(Current Ebay Oddities)</a> by Steve B, <a href=\"/Computer_Chess_Forums\" title=\"Computer Chess Forums\">Hiarcs Forum</a>, October 23, 2007 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=209853\">Rybka Unbeatable In Tournament Play?</a> by Steve B, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 19, 2008</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=215719\">To Bryan Whitby</a> by Steve B, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 06, 2008&#160;» <a href=\"/index.php?title=Bryan_Whitby&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Bryan Whitby (page does not exist)\">Bryan Whitby</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=43443\">Blincoe Knows the Truth about CM3000</a> by <a href=\"/Fernando_Villegas\" title=\"Fernando Villegas\">Fernando Villegas</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 24, 2012</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Blincoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/10261668@N05/\">Flickr: Photo collection</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/10261668@N05/sets/\">Flickr: Photo collection Sets</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/10261668@N05/sets/72157626781472057/\">The History Of Dedicated Chess Computers</a></dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/10261668@N05/sets/72157600923817845/\">Printed Material On Chess Computers</a></dd></dl>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/resurrect_hiarcs.htm\">Competition Prize</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.hiarcs.com/index.htm\">HIARCS Chess Software for PC, Mac, Pocket PC, iPhone, iPod and Palm Chess</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/HIARCS\" title=\"HIARCS\">HIARCS</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Steve_Blincoe&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.stmintz.com/ccc/index.php?id=365258\">Re: amazing</a> by steven blincoe, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 15, 2004</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/10261668@N05/\">Flickr: Photo collection</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/EBay\">eBay from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301071020\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.007 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.007 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 57/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 130/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:4074-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301071020 and revision id 6454\n -->\n"
